ding for Early Learners</span> <span class="chip">Mentoring</span> </div> </div> <div id="BriefSummary">Dynamic early childhood educator with 5+ years experience integrating technology in K2 classrooms, expertise in lesson/curriculum design and STEM, and recognized leadership. Teacher of the Year 2021; recently completed a professional development sabbatical.</div> </section> <section id="workhistory"> <h2>Work History</h2> <div id="workhistoryentries"> <div class="workhistoryentry entry"> <h3 class="workhistoryentrytitle">Sabbatical Year</h3> <div class="meta"> <span class="org">N/A</span>  <span class="loc">N/A</span>  <span class="type">Personal/Professional Development</span> </div> <div> <span class="workhistoryentrylastyear">Present</span> - <span class="workhistoryentryfirstyear workshitoryenteryfirstyear">2023</span> - <span class="duration">Unknown</span> </div> <div class="meta"> <span>Subjects/Grades:</span> N/A  <span>Curriculum/Standards:</span> N/A  <span>Technologies:</span> N/A </div> <div><span>Skills</span></div> <div class="skills-list"> <div class="skill"><span class="name">SEL</span> - <span class="conf">6</span> / 10 - <span class="years">1 (inferred)</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Trauma-Informed Teaching</span> - <span class="conf">5</span> / 10 - <span class="years">1 (inferred)</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">AI in Education</span> - <span class="conf">5</span> / 10 - <span class="years">1 (inferred)</span></div> </div> <div class="desc"> <div class="block-label">Responsibilities</div> <ul> <li>Attended workshops on social-emotional learning, trauma-informed teaching, and AI tools for education while on personal sabbatical.</li> </ul> <div class="block-label">Achievements/Impact</div> <ul> <li>Kept skillset current during career pause through active professional development and training.</li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="workhistoryentry entry"> <h3 class="workhistoryentrytitle">Kindergarten Technology Teacher & Team Lead</h3> <div class="meta"> <span class="org">Springfield Elementary School</span>  <span class="loc">Springfield, IL, USA</span>  <span class="type">Full-time</span> </div> <div> <span class="workhistoryentrylastyear">2023</span> - <span class="workhistoryentryfirstyear workshitoryenteryfirstyear">2018</span> - <span class="duration">4.9 years</span> </div> <div class="meta"> <span>Subjects/Grades:</span> Kindergarten (Ages 47), K2 code club  <span>Curriculum/Standards:</span> Not specified  <span>Technologies:</span> SMART Board, Computer Literacy, Coding Tools, ClassDojo, Seesaw </div> <div><span>Skills</span></div> <div class="skills-list"> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Technology Integration</span> - <span class="conf">9</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Team Leadership</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Curriculum Development</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">SMART Board</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Lesson Design</span> - <span class="conf">9</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Classroom Management</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Parent Communication</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">STEM</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Coding for Early Learners</span> - <span class="conf">7</span> / 10 - <span class="years">4</span></div> <div class="skill"><span class="name">Mentoring</span> - <span class="conf">8</span> / 10 - <span class="years">5