eriences and credentials she currently doesn''t have.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span> <span class="text">Scored slightly below the consensus to extra-emphasize the real magnitude of the domain and experience gap for this role.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Do not advance to interview for this position</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'a504e78d-4e7a-4fc7-baba-562528b506e3', N'd0617c28-c7db-4f51-a14e-2035dad9f354', N'661093a4-797b-47bc-a86b-59bd1e06ceef', 4, 1)
