adge score-green">91.5%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-negative">-0.55%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Taylor highlights Allens stand-out curriculum leadership, measurable results, and mentoring strength, factoring in a balance between school culture-building and minor grade-level or licensure gaps. Advocates for her hire while noting these limited reservations.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Taylors match is slightly under the overall due to consistent weight given to technical/regional specificity, though ultimately recognizes her exceptional overall value.</span></div></div><div class="agent" id="agent-Jordan"><div class="agent-name">Jordan Lee</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-green">88.25%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-negative">-3.8%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Jordan provides the most technical and cautious perspective, aligning heavily with region- and grade-level specific recency, while still recognizing Jennifers data-driven impact, curriculum mastery, and low-risk, high-reward teacher profile.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Jordans match is lower than the consensus due to stronger emphasis on direct, recent Texas standards and grades 25 classroom experience.</span></div></div><div class="agent" id="agent-Sunny"><div class="agent-name">Sunny Sam</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-green score-95plus">96.4%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+4.35%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Sunny foregrounds Jennifers unique faculty unification power, student/teacher success, and rare blend of curricular mastery and team-buildingthe ''spark'' a founding team needs. Emphasizes immediate cultural, instructional, and retention value.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Sunnys score is higher due to prioritizing school culture, team cohesion, and long-term faculty impact even above technical recency.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Move forward to final interview and references check; minimal onboarding for Texas standards recommended.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'186b2442-87c5-4dae-a9d6-5498a4fb4448', N'9cba86dd-c7e4-41d5-aef1-830dc82a176f', N'b85f6bf6-d1d1-4946-9f55-6ed6307185b7', 1, 2)
