gative">-0.2%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Jennifer is an evidence-based, high-skill educator with outstanding results in student achievement, curriculum, and staff mentoring. However, credential and Spanish gaps lower immediate fit. She would be ideal for a district ready to invest in bridging those gaps.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">A near-match with the consensus, as I balance credential requirements with Jennifers documented mentoring and student performance impact.</span></div></div><div class="agent" id="agent-Sunny Sam"><div class="agent-name">Sunny Sam</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-orange">77.4%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+0.6%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">I remain most optimistic about Jennifers lasting positive effect on school community and staff culture. She checks nearly all boxes except credential and Spanish, which will require early-stage investment from the school. If that support is given, she will shine.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">My score sits modestly above consensus, reflecting emphasis on cultural and morale benefits, and confidence in her trainability and community-building skills.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Recommend advancing to interview, with clarifying questions on willingness to transfer California credential and develop Spanish proficiency via professional learning. If immediate compliance is required, consider for future opportunities or with onboarding supports.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'186b2442-87c5-4dae-a9d6-5498a4fb4448', N'31951735-d8e3-4f4a-961f-84628e991dc3', N'112bc8a5-9d7b-408e-a5d9-fc92f560f9c7', 3, 2)
