s="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-yellow">38.2%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-negative">-3.2%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Jane exudes warmth, creativity, and a growth mindset. However, without tangible AP/high school math or departmental team leadership, her fit for this advanced, outcome-driven high school math role is low, despite her strong K-8 and community skills.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Sunny Sam places highest emphasis on the requisite specialized content and team-leadership skills, thus assigning the lowest rating in line with the technical gaps.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Do not proceed to interview; seek candidates with current secondary/AP math expertise and departmental leadership.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'55279827-be0a-42ce-ba93-ec3d0ffb4656', N'd0617c28-c7db-4f51-a14e-2035dad9f354', N'3474ca1a-eae6-420d-89a8-dbaa359ef866', 4, 3)
