ore-yellow">52.10%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+2.03%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Samantha exhibits vibrant classroom and curriculum skills, and her cultural/inclusive strengths are strong. Yet her lack of science content experience requires significant investment for independent program launch. She is an asset for broad teaching roles, but not an instant fit for science subject-leader.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Taylors score is marginally higher to reflect a slightly more optimistic view of Samanthas adaptability and long-term value, though still weighed down by the science expertise gap.</span></div></div><div class="agent" id="agent-JordanLee"><div class="agent-name">Jordan Lee</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-yellow">44.80%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-negative">-5.27%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Samantha''s classroom management, curriculum innovation, and inclusion are exceptional, but her lack of elementary science content knowledge and experience is a concrete barrier for this founding role. This score is more conservative, emphasizing the critical need for subject fluency.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Jordans match is lower owing to strict prioritization of the science requirement, which Samantha does not meet, thereby increasing perceived onboarding cost and program risk.</span></div></div><div class="agent" id="agent-SunnySam"><div class="agent-name">Sunny Sam</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-yellow">53.90%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+3.83%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Samanthas warmth, creativity, and whole-child mindset would boost any founding culture. However, her immediate readiness for leading science, especially hands-on/NGSS-aligned work, is lacking. Her score is still positive given the intangibles she brings to school launch.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Sunny maintains a higher score based on valuing culture, creativity, and long-term fit, though concedes the science subject-matter gap creates real program delays if she were selected.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Consider for generalist, co-teacher, or culture leadership roles, but recommend seeking candidates with proven science content expertise for the founding science position.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'7b2eac48-1530-4897-96c1-bf9810db8c98', N'9cba86dd-c7e4-41d5-aef1-830dc82a176f', N'480da846-053b-49b5-b6d7-8fb6d2806796', 1, 4)
