-name">Sunny Sam</div><div class="agent-match-line"><span class="label">Match:</span><span class="score-badge score-orange">72.25%</span><span class="label">? vs Overall:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+2.05%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Jessicas EdTech leadership, culture-building enthusiasm, and collaborative spirit set her apart for a new school. Her fit for upper elementary science is limited by content gaps, but her spark and potential for growth as a founding faculty are exceptional. With mentoring, she can close the content gap.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Sunny weights school-culture and growth mindset more heavily, thus granting Jessica a higher score. The science-content gap is acknowledged but more heavily offset by optimism about her long-term benefit to team and culture.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Recommend interview for foundational/tech-integrator or lower-grades role; clarify onboarding plan for science content if pursuing for grades 25 science.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'd4bc3c1d-08e0-4f78-9a9f-7631946e287a', N'9cba86dd-c7e4-41d5-aef1-830dc82a176f', N'a1713609-bc68-4050-868d-95f9967396ea', 1, 5)
