:</span><span class="diff diff-positive">+1.37%</span></div><div class="agent-justification"><span class="label">Justification:</span><span class="text">Jessicas spark, EdTech coaching, and team spirit show best in early elementary. However, the need for high school math subject-matter excellence, AP instruction, and department oversight goes unmet. Her strengths, though real, are for another context.</span></div><div class="agent-diff-reason" style="margin-top:6px;"><span class="label">Reason for difference from overall match:</span><span class="text">Score is slightly higher than overall due to some consideration of her collaborative and coaching strengths, but final weighting recognizes that subject-matter and leadership gaps are simply too profound.</span></div></div></div></section><section class="section" id="next-steps"><div class="section-header">Recommended Next Steps</div><div class="section-body next-steps"><div class="recommendation">Do not advance; seek a candidate with demonstrated high school math content, AP teaching, and departmental leadership experience.</div><div class="footnote">Note: Recommendations are based on the overall match and agent inputs. Adjust as needed with additional context or updated information.</div></div></section></main></body></html>', N'', N'd4bc3c1d-08e0-4f78-9a9f-7631946e287a', N'd0617c28-c7db-4f51-a14e-2035dad9f354', N'1914e587-d241-4e5a-8933-f61cf11f3deb', 4, 5)
