tion confidence) meet minimums but do not exceed them. While she is skilled in differentiation and communication with families, explicit experience with bilingual/inclusive urban classrooms and structured data-driven assessment/reporting for large groups is not documented. She would bring a warm, collaborative energy to the team, and could thrive with mentorship and formal upskilling.', N'This is my first evaluation for Jane and the role, so there is no previous match to adjust from. The 68.70 score weights her deep teaching, nurturing approach, and community contributions against missing required credentials, Spanish, and recent direct middle school classroom experience.', 11, 11, N'2fdc8eac-838c-43b9-a5f1-9f6dc16e237b', 34, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
