r 64.5%reflects a firmer weighting on credential/licensure requirements and the absence of Spanish and middle-level subject expertise, per consensus among reviewing agents.', 15, 15, N'2fdc8eac-838c-43b9-a5f1-9f6dc16e237b', 34, CAST(-2.00 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
