rgeted context. The resume shows little evidence of data-driven instruction, family engagement in a secondary context, or promoting advanced math outcomes. Jane''s longevity is high and she offers cost-saving potential as a stable, reliable, adaptable educator, but is unlikely to be ''plug and play'' for a high school math department lead. Additional training and content upskilling would be needed, raising onboarding costs and risks of mismatched placement.', N'This is the initial evaluation, so no adjustment has been made.', 1, 1, N'3474ca1a-eae6-420d-89a8-dbaa359ef866', 35, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
