xt, or demonstrated ability to teach or supervise advanced STEM curriculum. There are also no concrete metrics or outcomes related to high school math achievement or team leadership at the department level.', N'This is the initial evaluation and so no adjustment is applied.', 2, 2, N'3474ca1a-eae6-420d-89a8-dbaa359ef866', 35, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
