 in a role that specifically demands it, thus justifying a lowered match.', N'Adjustment downward results from post-initial calibration to ensure the match scoring more stringently reflects the absolute necessity for science subject-matter expertise for this particular role. This gap is even more pronounced when benchmarked against purpose-built founding science candidates.', 6, 6, N'480da846-053b-49b5-b6d7-8fb6d2806796', 36, CAST(-2.70 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
