idence of formal science content expertise, elementary-level science instruction, or related certifications. Relevant pedagogical strengths (curriculum design, differentiation, classroom management, technology integration) are present and verified, but cannot substitute for direct science content knowledge, which is non-negotiable for independent program leadership in this science-specific role.', N'This is the initial scoring, with no prior match percentage set in the conversation.', 10, 10, N'480da846-053b-49b5-b6d7-8fb6d2806796', 36, CAST(0.00 AS Decimal(5, 2)))
